		"description": "<p>You gain proficiency with a type of vehicle, or an expertise die if you are already proficient. You may spend 1 exertion to reroll a failed ability check related to vehicular activity, such as tool checks to repair a vehicle, Acrobatics checks to keep balance on a moving vehicle, or Animal Handling checks to calm animals drawing a vehicle. Likewise, if you are piloting a vehicle, you may spend 2 exertion to reroll a saving throw made by the vehicle. In both cases, you may choose whether to use the new roll or the original.</p>",
